casebody.data:
The PEOPLE etc., Respondent,
v.
Ramee MCCULLUM, Appellant. Motion No: 2019-355 Court of Appeals of New York. Decided May 2, 2019

*144Motion by The Community Development Project of the Urban Justice Center, et al. for leave to file a brief amici curiae on the appeal herein granted and the proposed brief is accepted as filed. The brief must be submitted in digital format within seven days.
